#prompt user for input

>help => displays all valid commands
>quit => quits
>subscriptions => displays all live subscribed streams
>subscriptions -a => displays all subscribed channels
>top => shows top livestreams on twitch
>top -g => shows top games on twitch
>search -c => searches channels
>search -g => searches games
>search -s => searches livestreams
>next => displays next page of results
>prev => displays previous page of results
>back => exits current function
>view => opens stream if channel is live or is stream, shows vods if channel not live, displays live streams if game

#extra features
>chat => displays chat
>chat -p => opens popout chat in firefox
>say => prints to stream chat if stream is live
